1
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:37,080
Go to the Tiangong Club now.

2
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
Around 4:00 p.m.,

3
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:41,610
the person in the photo will appear there.

4
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:43,880
Through the punk in the photo,

5
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:46,320
find his boss, Brother Hei,

6
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:48,320
and mention a name to him:

7
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:49,360
Wang Yu.

8
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:51,600
He'll know what it means.

9
00:00:52,080 --> 00:00:52,680
[Fishing]

10
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:44,280
Who are you?

11
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,800
I'm talking to you.

12
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,800
Can't you hear me?

13
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,840
You got some nerve,

14
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,200
selling goods on my turf.

15
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,480
Who on earth are you?

16
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,730
What are you talking about?

17
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:18,640
Oh.

18
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:19,640
I got it.

19
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,520
You had a few drinks

20
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:24,130
and came here to make trouble, huh?

21
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,880
You want to know who I am?

22
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:29,060
You don't deserve to know.

23
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,840
Take me to Brother Hei,

24
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,160
and let him talk to me.

25
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,600
Boss.

26
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:43,280
Is there some misunderstanding?

27
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,260
How about this?

28
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:46,720
Let me take a look.

29
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:49,090
What kind of good stuff do you have?

30
00:04:43,159 --> 00:04:43,960
Get her.

31
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,720
Don't hit women.

32
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,120
You.

33
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,040
Get up.

34
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,760
Chase them.

35
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:23,640
Go back and get in the car.

36
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,480
Chase them.

37
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,680
What's wrong?

38
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:00,440
I don't smoke.

39
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,040
Thanks.

40
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:10,440
No.

41
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:17,040
What's the beef between you and that guy?

42
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,360
It's fine.

43
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,200
No need to type.

44
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,680
I've interacted with deaf people before.

45
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,320
I can understand your sign language.

46
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,000
Go ahead.

47
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:35,840
He got my sister pregnant and won't take responsibility.

48
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,650
Then he deserves a beating.

49
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,320
I just checked.

50
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:42,960
The nearest gas station is two kilometers away.

51
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:45,360
You should figure something out yourself.

52
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,120
I have things to do.

53
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,200
I'll be going now.

54
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,160
They have more people.

55
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,290
Don't be impulsive.

56
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,960
You want to run after hitting me?

57
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,440
Can you escape?

58
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,920
Why don't you think about why they hit you?

59
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:17,000
Yeah.

60
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,560
Why did they hit me?

61
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,840
You have to ask her.

62
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,800
You got her sister pregnant.

63
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,240
Don't you deserve a beating?

64
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:24,760
What?

65
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:27,600
No way.

66
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,850
We all just came out to have fun.

67
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:31,720
No.

68
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,250
And why did you do it?

69
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,360
Who are you?

70
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,760
Why did you help her hit my men?

71
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,920
I already made it very clear who I am.

72
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,080
As for why I hit you,

73
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,680
it's because you hit a woman.

74
00:07:44,159 --> 00:07:45,920
I can't accept that at all.

75
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:48,220
Alright, it's not a major injury.

76
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:49,640
Just bear with it.

77
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,890
Let's get down to business.

78
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,159
Take me to your boss.

79
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,440
Wait.

80
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:58,120
My business with her is not over yet.

81
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,600
I don't care if she's a man or a woman.

82
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,640
Or if she did it for her sister.

83
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,200
She beat my hand like this.

84
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,980
If I don't get payback,

85
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,920
how will I survive?

86
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,280
Brothers.

87
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:12,880
Get him.

88
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,840
I said it before.

89
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:30,000
I hate hitting women the most.

90
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,250
Can we get down to business now?

91
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:53,720
Hei.

92
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,780
I'm done pounding.

93
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,320
Houzi,

94
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,160
how many times?

95
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:57,960
10,003 times.

96
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:01,200
Didn't I say 10,000 times?

97
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:02,920
Not one more,

98
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,040
not one less.

99
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,900
You did three extra times.

100
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:07,460
How am I supposed to eat it?

101
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:08,440
Hei,

102
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,320
please spare me.

103
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,440
I really can't pound anymore.

104
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,000
My hands won't listen to me.

105
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,800
Since they won't listen,

106
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,930
you don't need them.

107
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:19,840
Continue.

108
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,680
You must be Mr. Hei.
